  <p>Converts <code>color</code> to the HLS format.</p>  <p>The <code>hue</code> value is in the 0 .. 360 range. The <code>luminance</code> and
<code>saturation</code> values are in the 0 .. 1 range.</p>
  <p>Since 1.16</p>
